org.gvsig.gpe.xml
Class XmlProperties

java.lang.Object
  org.gvsig.gpe.xml.XmlProperties
All Implemented Interfaces:
IGPEProperties
public class XmlProperties
extends java.lang.Object
implements IGPEProperties

This class contains the properties for the XML parsers and writers. This class has been registered using the SPI (Service Provider Interface) and the values of their properties can be configured using GPEDefaults.

DEFAULT_BLANC_SPACE

public static final java.lang.String DEFAULT_BLANC_SPACE
Character to replace the blank spaces in the names that has to be added like a XML node. On the writing process all the blank spaces are replaced by this character and on the reading process this character is replaced by a blank space.
